<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٧٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6702">هِشَامٍ </a>حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">أَبِي، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> كُفِّنَ فِي ثَلَاثَةِ أَثْوَابٍ، لَيْسَ فِيهَا قَمِيصٌ وَلَا عِمَامَةٌ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>